driven through brown fields exploration on its existing land positions and through opportunistic ma in the same regions its chairperson is cheryl carolus and the ceo is nick holland contents  board of directors  executive directors  operations  australia  ghana  peru  south africa  bibliography  references  external links board of directorsedit chairman – cheryl carolus executive directorsedit chief executive officer – nicholas j holland holland has worked in financial management for  years  years of which were spent in the mining sector he has been an executive at gold fields since  becoming ceo in  holland is also a director of the rand refinery one of the worlds largest gold refineries chief financial officer – paul a schmidt operationsedit australiaedit agnew gold mine st ives gold mine granny smith gold mine darlot gold mine ghanaedit tarkwa gold mine km west of the town of tarkwa damang gold mine km north of the neighbouring tarkwa gold mine peruedit cerro corona gold mine the cerro corona mine in peru is in the highest part of the western cordillera of the andes mountains in the north of the country south africaedit south deep gold mine bibliographyedit gold fields a centenary portrait by paul johnson writer many black and white colour plates of personnel and topography includes an image of guy carleton jones and refers to consolidated gold fields and its subsidiary companies referencesedit  httpzanewsyahoocomcarolustakesovergoldfieldschairwomanfinancehtml  a b c profiless stock exchange handbook october  – january  johannesburg south africa sasfin  p  issn    simon walker gold new fundamentals engineering  mining journal feb  v n p  a b gold fields company website gold fields retrieved  september    published by weidenfeld and nicolson london in  with isbn  external linksedit gold fields limited this south african corporation or company article is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlegoldfieldsol